An antidote?

34
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:57,280
You saved me?

35
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,360
Xiyao and I learned of this

36
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,840
when we came to give you

37
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,470
the wedding invitation.

38
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:13,590
The crown prince was willing

39
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,520
