51
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,510
Qing. You should rest.

52
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:33,950
I'm all right.

53
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,560
Yao.

54
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:41,240
Can I have a word with the crown prince

55
00:04:41,390 --> 00:04:42,600
