118
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:40,440
No one should criticize you.

119
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:46,360
Whatever you've done,

120
00:08:47,270 --> 00:08:49,750
I know you won't
repeat the same mistakes.

121
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:05,510
Ji Chu.

122
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:07,200
