123
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:09,120
You should be resting.

124
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,840
I could be worried.

125
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,960
Do you know

126
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,360
