169
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:03,040
[Prince Lv Residence]

170
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,120
Your Highness.

171
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,240
While I monitored

172
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,120
Imperial Consort Wei,

173
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,910
