196
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,630
In that case,

197
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:13,480
based on the novel's story,

198
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:14,790
he and Ji Chu

199
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,750
