235
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:56,480
Did you run into any danger

236
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,080
on your way here?

237
00:14:01,270 --> 00:14:02,600
Thanks to your protection,

238
00:14:02,870 --> 00:14:04,630
we had a safe journey.

239
00:14:05,870 --> 00:14:08,120
We'll discuss the details inside.

240
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,440
This is embarrassing!

241
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:15,200
I met my love rival

242
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:16,200
looking like a total mess!

243
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:19,480
That was a total disaster.

244
00:14:20,510 --> 00:14:21,200
No.

245
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,390
How can I salvage this?

246
00:14:22,390 --> 00:14:23,750
Your Highness, where have you been?

247
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:24,960
I was going to

248
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:26,000
groom you just now.

249
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,480
That's it! Mo Yu,

250
00:14:28,630 --> 00:14:29,200
quick.

251
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:30,550
I need my makeup now.

252
00:14:30,790 --> 00:14:31,790
Let's go.

253
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,270
Chu.

254
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:35,840
After you left Nanjing,

255
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:37,440
the factions there

256
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:38,840
were eager to make a move.

257
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:41,270
Prime Minister Li Dianzhao

258
00:14:41,550 --> 00:14:43,480
even planned to usurp the throne.

259
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:46,080
He is forming cliques.

260
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:48,870
