your ability as a regent.

261
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:50,150
He spread rumors

262
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,550
that you conspired with hostile nations

263
00:14:52,550 --> 00:14:54,320
and were in contact
with Prince Lv to exchange

264
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:55,390
information.

265
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:57,200
I did as you said.

266
00:14:57,510 --> 00:14:58,270
I tried to dissolve

267
00:14:58,270 --> 00:14:59,510
Li Dianzhao's faction.

268
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,000
But I didn't think

269
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:03,030
