272
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:10,000
and sent him to Liang.

273
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:15,120
A nation cannot last without its ruler.

274
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:17,200
By sending him here,

275
00:15:18,030 --> 00:15:19,600
you put yourself in greater harm.

276
00:15:19,910 --> 00:15:21,480
It was the only way I could think of.

277
00:15:22,030 --> 00:15:23,670
Nanqing draws
too much attention in Nanjing.

278
00:15:23,870 --> 00:15:25,150
You're the only one who can help us.

279
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:26,200
According to my agent,

280
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,550
Li Dianzhao branded you the traitor,

281
00:15:29,790 --> 00:15:31,670
claiming that you wanted to kill Nanqing

282
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,960
to usurp the throne.

283
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:36,200
His claims have made waves in the city.

284
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:37,960
You two

285
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:39,200
should stay here

286
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:40,510
to wait it out.

287
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:42,600
We'll discuss our next course of action.

288
00:15:45,910 --> 00:15:47,390
But with no one in the Imperial Court,

289
00:15:48,870 --> 00:15:50,960
Li Dianzhao might use
this chance to rebel.

290
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:53,910
Don't worry about that.

291
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:56,150
Li Dianzhao won't get
the throne for now.

292
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,320
How so?

293
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,320
Nanyi,

294
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:06,910
do you have

295
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:08,630
the Fish-shaped Token on you?

